sure the model's robustness against future, unseen data, reflecting the sequential nature of football matches." "Evaluation Metrics: Model performance was evaluated using metrics such as:" "Accuracy (overall correct predictions)" "Log Loss (for probabilistic predictions)" "F1-score (for each class: Home, Draw, Away)" "Confusion Matrix (to analyze misclassifications)" "Profit/Loss (if you simulated betting strategies based on predictions)" Installation Provide clear instructions on how to set up the project environment.
